nf_ingredient_statement: Whole Grain Rice, Rice, Sugar, Fructose, Canola And/Or Rice Bran Oil, Salt, Cinnamon, Molasses. Vitamin E (Mixed Tocopherols) And BHT Added to Preserve Freshness. Vitamins And Minerals: Calcium Carbonate, Iron And Zinc (Mineral Nutrients), Vitamin C (Sodium Ascorbate), A B Vitamin (Niacinamide), Vitamin B6 (Pyridoxine Hydrochloride), Vitamin B1 (Thiamin Mononitrate), Vitamin A (Palmitate), Vitamin B2 (Riboflavin), A B Vitamin (Folic Acid), Vitamin B12, Vitamin D3.
